# Uber Taxi Fare Prediction â€“ Machine Learning Regression Project

This project focuses on predicting taxi fare prices for Uber rides using a supervised machine learning approach. The goal is to build a regression model capable of estimating fare amounts based on trip characteristics such as pickup/dropoff coordinates, passenger count, and trip distance.

The project includes exploratory data analysis (EDA), feature engineering, data cleaning, model training, evaluation, and a prediction interface.

