## ğŸš• 1. Project Overview

Uber provides millions of rides every day, generating large amounts of trip data. Accurate fare prediction systems help:

- Improve customer transparency  
- Optimize pricing models  
- Detect unusual ride patterns  
- Reduce fraud and miscalculations  

This project builds a regression pipeline to predict fare amounts using the publicly available Uber Taxi Fare dataset.

